pipelineConfig.title: DP4BI_DEV_OHPNM_CDC_RESYNC
pipelineConfig.description: Compare the number of records between OHPNM tables and Snowflake Tables

configuration.name: preprocessScript
query
configuration.value:
select s.name as TABLE_SCHEMA, t.name as TABLE_NAME--, STR_TO_DATE(date_format(current_timestamp(),'%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS LOG_CREATED_ON
from sys.tables t join sys.schemas s on t.schema_id = s.schema_id
where t.type = 'U' and 
      ((s.name = 'audit' and t.name = 'A_CREDENTIALING')
        or 
	   (s.name = 'dbo' and
         (t.name in (
 'A_CREDENTIALING'
,'APPLICATION_FEE_PAYMENT_TYPE'
,'APPLICATION_FEE_WAIVER_REASON'
,'APPLICATION_STATUS'
,'APPLICATION_TYPE'
,'COMMUNICATION_EVENT'
,'COMMUNICATION_EVENT_TYPE'
,'COMMUNICATIONEVENT_PARTY_REG_XREF'
,'CREDENTIAL_ACTIVITY'
,'CREDENTIALING'
,'Credentialing_Provider_Specialty_Type'
,'Credentialing_Provider_Specialty_Type_Mapping'
,'CREDENTIALING_PROVIDER_TYPE'
,'CREDENTIALING_RESULT'
,'CREDENTIALING_STATUS'
,'EMAIL'
,'reg_application'
,'REG_APPLICATION_FEE'
,'REG_BACKGROUND_CHECK'
,'REG_CREDENTIALING'
,'REG_MEDICAID'
,'REG_MEDICARE'
,'REG_OWNER'
,'REG_PROGRAM_STATUS_TYPE'
,'REG_PROVIDER'
,'REG_PROVIDER_DISENROLLMENT'
,'REG_PROVIDER_NOTE_XREF'
,'REG_PROVIDER_SERVICES_STATUS_TYPE'
,'REG_PROVIDER_STATUS_TYPE'
,'REG_SPECIALTY'
,'REGISTRATION'
,'REGISTRATION_STATUS_TYPE'
,'REGISTRATION_USER_XREF'
,'SCREENING'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_DEFAULT_TEMPLATE'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_OWNER_TEMPLATE'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_RISK_LEVEL_TEMPLATE'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_STATUS'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_TYPE'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_TYPE_STATUS_XREF'
,'SCREENING_ACTIVITY_TYPE_URL'
,'SCREENING_ADVERSE_ACTION'
,'SCREENING_EVENT_TYPE'
,'SCREENING_METHOD'
,'SCREENING_RESULT'
,'SCREENING_STATUS'
,'SITE_VISIT'
,'SITE_VISIT_ATTEMPT'
,'SITE_VISIT_ATTEMPT_STATUS'
,'SITE_VISIT_ATTEMPT_TYPE'
,'SITE_VISIT_FINDINGS'
,'SITE_VISIT_METHOD'
,'SITE_VISIT_RECOMMENDATION'
,'SITE_VISIT_RESULT'
,'SITE_VISIT_SCREENING'
,'SITE_VISIT_SCREENING_STATUS'
,'SITE_VISIT_SCREENING_TYPE'
,'SITE_VISIT_STATUS'
,'SITE_VISIT_TYPE'
,'USER_ACCOUNT_INFORMATION'
,'USER_AGENT_REG_XREF'
,'USER_AGENT_ROLE_XREF'
,'WF_ACTION'
,'WF_PARAMETER'
,'WF_PROCESS'
,'WF_STEP'
,'WF_TASK'
,'WF_TASK_GROUP'
,'WF_WORKFLOW'
         ))
        )
	)		 
order by 2;
